Package: CohortContrast
Type: Package
Title: Feature Selection and Enrichment Analysis for OMOP CDM Cohorts
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Markus Haug <markus.haug@ut.ee>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Markus", "Haug", , "markus.haug@ut.ee", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0935-3307")),
    person("Raivo", "Kolde", , "raivo.kolde@ut.ee", 
    role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2886-6298"))
    )
Description: Defines target and control cohorts and extracts medical interventions
    that are over-represented in the target cohort during the observation period.
    Users can tune filtering and selection with arguments such as topK, presenceFilter,
    and prevalenceCutOff. The workflow includes CHI2Y tests (chi-squared tests for
    two proportions with Yates continuity correction), logistic tests, and optional
    visual exploration helpers.
